{"tid":1068904,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"T.O.P當兵中又出事！ 被爆「軍中耍特權」病假請了同僚3倍","createTime":"2019-03-19T14:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T12:29:00.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"192338882c3bdb59866aec19e1a21bdf7acd1b40","tid":1068904,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"南韓天團BIGBANG近年來風波不斷，前成員勝利被爆在「老司機群組」內看偷拍淫片，引爆後續一連串風波，他也為此宣布退出演藝圈。然而當兵中的成員們也不得安寧，19日晚間韓媒報導，成員T.O.P（本名：崔勝鉉）目前以「社會服務要員」服役中，卻被爆享有藝人特權狂請病假。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3968/d3968952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3968%2Fd3968952.jpg&h=9b6bab76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲T.O.P走過呼麻風波，卻又被爆軍中耍特權。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\n19日晚間南韓MBC電視台《NEWSDESK》節目獨家揭露，經歷呼麻風波後，目前以「社會服務要員」服役中的T.O.P，卻享有比其他同僚更多的病假，且請假日都在「休息日」過後。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3950/d3950239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3950%2Fd3950239.jpg&h=8c309414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲勝利已經宣布退出BIGBANG。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\nMBC調查發現，在同一地區「龍山區廳」的社會服務要員共有226名，規定「除了重大疾病和事故等不得已的情況外」不得請假，但T.O.P使用病假的次數是平均值的3倍，而休息日前後的病假更是平均值的4倍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3134/d3134727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3134%2Fd3134727.jpg&h=19dadae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲G-Dragon在軍中也被爆享有特權。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\n今年2月G-Dragon也同樣被爆料，服役了364天，卻有100多天（包含住院期間）都在軍隊外度過，幾乎佔據三分之一的兵役日子。為此軍方替他緩頰，「去除病假以外，他的休假皆是按照一般服役士兵的規定假期來休，沒有問題。」YG娛樂當時則是回應「無話可說」。"},{"pid":"69c5ce4009dc92c17d69fb711d5d0dda8e883731","tid":1068904,"uid":23021,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"道友身子係弱d"},{"pid":"7790ee8c81a8a1fc3493190b6bce15b8ca35fbc0","tid":1068904,"uid":43061,"like":23,"dislike":15,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"病能左都唔比牙?<br />\n有晒醫生紙WO<br />\n旺角藥房20蚊張<br />\n我介紹TOP去買的"},{"pid":"0a250b2e0ee88fa513bf1fef9b40634c9e20d655","tid":1068904,"uid":193951,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"喺無任何實質證據之前 我係唔會相信呢啲謠言"},{"pid":"1fc1a21d927df8bd32e360a0e1d47f87ff02f8e2","tid":1068904,"uid":63057,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"bigbang明顯被人針住屈<br />\n之前gd又係"},{"pid":"64deb0bf06eec6d0532954c26ab2dfbcf96fdcfa","tid":1068904,"uid":213300,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"呢排我BB成日被人屈<br />\n真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb9764452360798141f5398bf970acdc97d9363","tid":1068904,"uid":231908,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:28:49.000Z","msg":"BIG GANG<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddd214c26f3f526aec3ca9c617447c331b9f0ec","tid":1068904,"uid":225636,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"人不嬲都有三六九等架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毒撚廢青同當紅巨星都要一樣要求<br />\n咁先真係唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：毒撚廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec4cc434340356264a4ba1b24578e63907f3a8c","tid":1068904,"uid":87394,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"呀sir比請咪得囉<br />\n咪多事啦"},{"pid":"4fd718717f2cf759a860f90ace7bc0a3e990b01b","tid":1068904,"uid":188751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:59:05.000Z","msg":"T.O.P 一向都有老架喎，成班粉絲都知架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人到底有幾想整死YG"},{"pid":"e786d1e